title: ArcGIS Server Machine
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: MIT
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors the configured state and realtime state of ArcGIS Server
 machines.

 A machine can be configured as STARTED or STOPPED, while the realtime state
 shows what the machine is actually doing. The rule parameters control how
 mismatches and transitional states are mapped to Checkmk states.
item:
 The ArcGIS Server machine name.
discovery:
 One service is discovered for each ArcGIS Server machine returned by the Server
 admin API.
